ษออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออป
บ                      THROUGH MY EYES                               บ
บ                                                                    บ
บ         Through my eyes I have seen this world                     บ
บ         Each time it's as if I have never saw it before            บ
บ         Always finding something new to make it beautiful          บ
บ                                                                    บ
บ         I have seen it through the eyes of a child                 บ
บ         A place of wonder and knowledge                            บ
บ         So secure with the love of a mother and a father           บ
บ                                                                    บ
บ         Then once more I saw my world as a teen                    บ
บ         No longer could it teach me anything                       บ
บ         For I thought I knew it all                                บ
บ                                                                    บ
บ         I'm now looking through eyes of a lover                    บ
บ         And everything is so beautiful                             บ
บ         Especially the man who gives me this love                  บ
บ                                                                    บ
บ         As a new mother my eyes, oh what they see                  บ
บ         I now see that this world has a lot to teach me            บ
บ         And in turn I must become the teacher                      บ
บ                                                                    บ
บ         My eyes are old and have seen it all                       บ
บ         From war to peace, birth to death, and everything          บ
บ                 in between                                         บ
บ         Now I will close my eyes for the last time, no             บ
บ                 more will they see                                 บ
บ                                                                    บ
บ                 (c)Catherine Cowan 8/13/92                         บ
บ                                                                    บ
